{"tid":1395552,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【未雨綢繆】打雨戰嘅戰術討論","createTime":"2019-08-01T19:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:53:08.000Z","uid":259980,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"717e8c232c55d34806fcf1d5d98d5318a6f596fd","tid":1395552,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:13:43.000Z","msg":"香港夏天多雨，唔難預測將來點都會有一、兩場抗爭係會落雨，但一落雨個<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">環境變化好大</span>，我地要對可能出現嘅情況作出估算同諗<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">應對方法</span>。<br />\n<br />\n落雨時嘅戰場：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1催淚彈、胡椒威力下降</span></span><br />\n<br />\n算係小優勢<br />\n因為本身都已經counter到胡椒同tg<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2地面濕滑</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兩邊都有阻礙<br />\n但一般嚟講人地衝<br />\n我地退<br />\n點都蝕底d<br />\n<br />\n對速龍應該影響更大<br />\n衝個陣會有所保留<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3能見度下降</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兩邊都睇唔清對方部署同人手流動<br />\n<br />\n兩邊遠攻都好難提防<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">傳媒鏡頭影唔清<br />\n極危險</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4聲音難以傳播</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地有walkie<br />\n我地無<br />\n劣勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">開槍變滅聲</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5對豬嘴/口罩有影響？</span></span>"},{"pid":"e857c361bd32198032832e260c02c6a94277af1a","tid":1395552,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:17:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bbf917c8b6268dcd1ca6526499ce6199600b6bd","tid":1395552,"uid":217416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:29:26.000Z","msg":"豬嘴個濾餅濕咗就收皮"},{"pid":"bec168d09fca9e636bd341eec049cffe0c9c7161","tid":1395552,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f5aedb1f0e372688acf2ff8e61b246d5f25f014","tid":1395552,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"我唔明次次都企定等人清有乜用?<br />\n點解唔敵進我退 be water?"}]}